  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/6c5abbe6d27f1aafc151a838c355cb1f.poster.avif?t=1735400323\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/6c5abbe6d27f1aafc151a838c355cb1f.webm?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/6c5abbe6d27f1aafc151a838c355cb1f.mp4?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wishlist the game if you find it interesting!❤️<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>In Fallen Force enemy is dead only if you punch him off the edge of arena. You have to use clever positioning, mix of fast light attacks with strong charged attacks and special abilities that grant you temporary edge over your enemies while avoiding getting punched yourself. Survive 20 rounds of endless enemy waves, upgrade yourself and become  an unstoppable force.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/422fb22b117a6a9496a2724ae9798492.poster.avif?t=1735400323\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/422fb22b117a6a9496a2724ae9798492.webm?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/422fb22b117a6a9496a2724ae9798492.mp4?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2>You have the option to create your own player. Choose one of many characters, weapons and abilities with thousands of options from the start and buy as many upgrades to create the most powerful build possible. Punch them, shoot them, burn them, freeze them and push your enemies out of arena whatever way you want, for that is the only way to win...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/9a4f0cef2054cf2c6a2807b1d0e70f1d.poster.avif?t=1735400323\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/9a4f0cef2054cf2c6a2807b1d0e70f1d.webm?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/9a4f0cef2054cf2c6a2807b1d0e70f1d.mp4?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/2a43835f6b6f676907c9e5c9d3faefb7.avif?t=1735400323\" width=606 height=179 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/6c5abbe6d27f1aafc151a838c355cb1f.poster.avif?t=1735400323\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/6c5abbe6d27f1aafc151a838c355cb1f.webm?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/6c5abbe6d27f1aafc151a838c355cb1f.mp4?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wishlist the game if you find it interesting!❤️<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>In Fallen Force enemy is dead only if you punch him off the edge of arena. You have to use clever positioning, mix of fast light attacks with strong charged attacks and special abilities that grant you temporary edge over your enemies while avoiding getting punched yourself. Survive 20 rounds of endless enemy waves, upgrade yourself and become  an unstoppable force.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/422fb22b117a6a9496a2724ae9798492.poster.avif?t=1735400323\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/422fb22b117a6a9496a2724ae9798492.webm?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/422fb22b117a6a9496a2724ae9798492.mp4?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2>You have the option to create your own player. Choose one of many characters, weapons and abilities with thousands of options from the start and buy as many upgrades to create the most powerful build possible. Punch them, shoot them, burn them, freeze them and push your enemies out of arena whatever way you want, for that is the only way to win...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/9a4f0cef2054cf2c6a2807b1d0e70f1d.poster.avif?t=1735400323\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/9a4f0cef2054cf2c6a2807b1d0e70f1d.webm?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/9a4f0cef2054cf2c6a2807b1d0e70f1d.mp4?t=1735400323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354920/extras/2a43835f6b6f676907c9e5c9d3faefb7.avif?t=1735400323\" width=606 height=179 /></span>",
